  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEND YOUR CASTLE.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your castle against tireless waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight in several worlds against thousands of golems that are willing to destroy your kingdom. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build an elaborate defense to restrain the hordes that assault you in each scenario.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE COMBINATIONS.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose wisely among 22 towers to rise an impenetrable barricade.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the power within the element fusions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It´s up to you to stop thousands of enemies.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PROGRESS AGAINST ALL ODDS.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place your towers anywhere in the map and choose the right combinations of elements to achieve victory.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through several worlds to discover why the golems have rised against you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691490/extras/d72fcd6159a72fa1b3d6e35aa929e558.poster.avif?t=1754750051\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691490/extras/d72fcd6159a72fa1b3d6e35aa929e558.webm?t=1754750051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691490/extras/d72fcd6159a72fa1b3d6e35aa929e558.mp4?t=1754750051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEND YOUR CASTLE.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your castle against tireless waves of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight in several worlds against thousands of golems that are willing to destroy your kingdom. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build an elaborate defense to restrain the hordes that assault you in each scenario.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE COMBINATIONS.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose wisely among 22 towers to rise an impenetrable barricade.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the power within the element fusions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It´s up to you to stop thousands of enemies.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PROGRESS AGAINST ALL ODDS.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place your towers anywhere in the map and choose the right combinations of elements to achieve victory.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance through several worlds to discover why the golems have rised against you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691490/extras/d72fcd6159a72fa1b3d6e35aa929e558.poster.avif?t=1754750051\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691490/extras/d72fcd6159a72fa1b3d6e35aa929e558.webm?t=1754750051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691490/extras/d72fcd6159a72fa1b3d6e35aa929e558.mp4?t=1754750051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
